  positive\, unstoppable tone for the hours ahead.\n\nEnjoy a Fun\, Energiz
 ing Warm-up: Wake up your muscles and mind with a dynamic warm-up that ge
 ts your blood pumping and prepares your body for movement.\n\nBuild Founda
 tion with Technique: We’ll introduce simple\, accessible jazz technique
  and exercises focused on strengthening your core and improving flexibi
 lity and coordination.\n\nLearn Feel-Good Choreography: Dive into short\,
  simple\, and joyful dance combinations designed to make you smile\, mov
 e your body\, and boost your mood instantly.\n\nCome dance\, sweat\, smile
 \, and find your rhythm! Leave the studio feeling lighter\, brighter\, and
