BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Chair Yoga with Lavender Lotus
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T140000
UID:260303oc78i6rWX0GmSpdAYJ_hWw
DESCRIPTION:Maintain and regain mobility in this gentle form of yoga that 
 is practiced while sitting on a chair. Gentle strengthening and stretching
  will be accompanied by breathwork and mindful movement. This class is des
 igned for seniors and individuals with limited mobility\, but all are welc
 ome. It will also be beneficial for desk workers to learn techniques that 
