 ces that shape daily life\, like housing\, public health\, wildfire prepar
 edness\, and transportation.\n\nDistrict 2 includes the cities of Petalum
 a and Cotati\, parts of Rohnert Park\, as well as the unincorporated commu
 nities of Penngrove\, Two Rock\, Bloomfield\, and parts of the unincorpora
 ted community south of Sebastopol.\n\nIf you live in one of these areas\, 
 this something you do not want to miss. The candidates running are John Ki
