DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T220000
UID:260401puuJ0npqWE-_G2urcUa4aw
DESCRIPTION:A live dating comedy show in San Francisco. Real singles. Live
  matchmaking. Participation optional. One night only!\n\n Sight Unseen: L
 ive Dating Comedy Show  Santa Rosa — One Night Only\n\nThis is not a no
 rmal comedy show.\n\nThroughout the night\, real audience members are brou
 ght on stage for blind-date style games while comedians roast\, comment\, 
 and stir the chaos live.\n\nSometimes it’s sweet. Sometimes it’s bruta
 lly awkward. It’s always hilarious.\n\nYou can volunteer to participate
 … or just sit back\, watch the madness\, and enjoy the show.\n\nExpect q
 uick stand-up sets\, crowd interaction\, and unpredictable moments that on
 ly happen in a small room.\n\n Tickets $15 General Admission (Limited)  
 $20 At The Door (if seats remain)\n\nHigh energy. Limited seating. Once th
 e room fills\, tickets are gone.\n\n 21+
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/sight-unseen-a-live-dating-comedy-show-sa
 nta-rosa-thursday-march-9-tickets-1985107905182?aff=oddtdtcreator
