 at tunes\, and golden-hour energy — this is what Thursdays in downtown S
 anta Rosa are all about.\n\n21+ only.  Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendoci
 no Ave\, downtown Santa Rosa.\n\nCheck out **www.BarrelProofLounge.com**
