 he Sonoma Valley Regional Library on Fridays February 6\, 13\, 20 & 27\, M
 arch 6\, 13\, 20\, & 27\, April 3 & 10. Register either by calling 707-996
 -5217 or in person at the library's service desk. Please provide a contact
