 et ready to enjoy a night of great music and good vibes. See you there! Op
 en Uke jam hosted by your friendly neighborhood Ukulele collective.\n\nBri
 ng your singing voice and your Uke if you've got one\, and enjoy the comfo
 rtable\, welcoming space at Barrel Proof Lounge!\n\n21\\+\n\nLive Music 3-
