DESCRIPTION:Get ready to rock n' roll all night with Glory Dayz in Downtow
 n Santa Rosa!\n\nJoin us for an unforgettable night at Glory Dayz feat. Fr
 ankie Adel of Sha Na Na - Live Rock n' Roll in Downtown Santa Rosa! Get re
 ady to rock out at Barrel Proof Lounge with the legendary Frankie Adel. It
 's going to be a night filled with classic tunes\, high energy\, and good 
 vibes. Don't miss out on this epic event!\n\nGlory Dayz celebrates the bes
 t of the best classic rock-n-roll music from the 60’s through the 2000
 ’s. With front man Frankie Adel - former lead singer from Sha Na Na - br
 inging his dynamic stage presence\, this band will keep you dancing all ni
 ght long. Our collective experience includes working with some of music’
 s greats such as: Celine Dion\, Hall & Oates\, Huey Lewis\, Beach Boys\, P
 aul Anka\, Kenny Rogers and more. Our goal is to ignite music memories fro
 m your own Glory Days. We fill the house with good vibes\, good crowds and
  rockin-good times!\n\n21+\n\nDoors@7 / Show@8\n\n$10adv / $15door\n\nChec
 k out BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge
