DESCRIPTION:*Where unforgettable wines\, live music\, and good vibes come 
 together.* \n\nJoin us every Saturday from 3–6 PM at Spicy Vines for a t
 asting room experience like no other — where top local musicians from ac
 ross the Bay Area meet our award-winning small-lot wines. From Rock & Roll
  and Blues to Jazz\, Bluegrass\, and Americana\, each weekend brings new s
 ounds and new reasons to raise a glass. \n\n**Quintessence Music Duo** Qu
 intessence is a married musical duo whose shared passion for performing an
 d songwriting creates a warm\, reflective soundscape that celebrates both 
 the ordinary and the extraordinary. \n\n**Details**\n\nNo cover. Walk-ins
