SUMMARY:Comedy Night at Konocti Vista Casino and Resort
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T213000
UID:260327HKfojU7T0EuoAayfGLcI-A
DESCRIPTION:Comedy Night at Konocti Vista Casino and Resort Venue: Konocti
  Vista Casino and Resort Address: 2755 Mission Rancheria Rd.\, Lakeport\, 
 CA Bar & Doors Open: 7:00 pm\, Saturday\, April 11th\, 2026 Showtime: 8:00
  pm to 9:30 pm Ticket Price: $20 fees apply \\(Includes a $10 matchplay wi
 th purchase\\) Purchase tickets online here: https://www.etix.com/ticket/p
 /62202936/comedy-night-barry-neal-and-jennifer-jolly-lakeport-konocti-vist
 a-event-center Headliner: Barry Neal Barry’s beginnings were unusual. Af
 ter graduating from Northwestern University and completing a successful ru
 n in the famous Mee-Ow show \\(who’s celebrity members have included Jul
 ia Louis Dreyfus\, Dermot Mulroney\, George Newborn\, Craig Bierko\, Seth 
 Meyers\, and Ana Gasteyer\\)\, his brother dared him to go onstage at an o
 pen mic to do a routine. Barry was hit that night\, and knew that stand-up
  comedy was his next mountain to climb. Barry’s style is clean\, high en
 ergy\, and relationship material was a hit in almost every market. He quic
 kly moved up the comedy ladder and was on cable and network tv\, from MTV\
 , NBC\, Comedy Central\, and VH-1. His Dry Bar Special\, Lawyer Up has bee
 n seen by over 500K viewers.  Barry’s act was noticed by a production co
 mpany that loved his Counselor of Love persona\, and his act is currently 
 being shopped as a sitcom called The Counselor of Love that Barry wrote al
 ong with his partner Dan Patterson\, who was creator and executive produce
 r of Who’s Line Is It Anyway?  Opener: Jennifer Jolly Jennifer Jolly per
 forms stand-up comedy all over America\, Europe\, & Asia\, but can be seen
  regularly in Los Angeles at The Comedy Store & The Hollywood Improv. She
 ’s also performed at San Francisco Sketchfest\, UC San Diego\, UC Irvine
 \, & at the MGM Grand in Las Vegas. You can catch her acting in various co
 mmercials\, TV shows\, & Indie films\, as well. Location: The show will be
  held in the exquisite Banquet Hall. Make sure to get there early for the 
 best seats. Bar Service: Quench your thirst before the show starts! Doors 
 and the bar open at 7 pm. Age Restriction: Attendees must be 21 or older. 
 Seating: Limited availability to ensure an intimate comedy experience. Sec
 ure your spot now by purchasing tickets online or at the Player’s Club. 
 Grab your tickets and prepare for an evening filled with laughter and top-
 notch entertainment!
LOCATION:Konocti Vista Casino Resort
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/1550538583739104/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
