 n one unforgettable afternoon. ✨\n\nJoin **Sing Napa Valley** for its an
 nual spring choral concert\, *Around the World in 80 Minutes*\, an uplifti
 ng celebration of cultures\, languages\, and the music that connects us al
 l. Conducted by **Ronnie Zanella**\, the choir brings the world to life th
 rough powerful songs in 9+ languages\, including Portuguese\, Zulu\, Hebre
 w\, Russian\, Lakota\, and Mandarin and more.\n\nFeel the joy\, longing\, 
 and hope woven into each piece. Be inspired by music that reminds us how d
 eeply connected we are — across borders\, cultures\, and generations. Th
 is is more than a concert\; it’s an experience you’ll carry with you l
 ong after the final note.\n\n🎟 **Reserve your seat now and travel the w
 orld through song:**  👉 https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/around-t
 he-world-in-80-minutes\n\nℹ️ **Learn more:**  https://www.singnapaval
 ley.org\n\n*Processing fees are optional.*
