DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260412T140000
UID:260317iz4LeoMDsE6eoGq95BLXUw
DESCRIPTION:Tap into your creative flow at **Mercy’s Puff N’ Paint**
 —where cannabis culture\, art\, and community come together in an elevat
 ed\, laid-back experience inside The Lounge at Mercy.\n\nPuff\, and paint 
 in a relaxed\, inspiring atmosphere designed to spark creativity and conne
 ction. Whether you’re focused on your canvas or vibing with the people a
 round you\, this paint session is all about expression\, conversation\, an
 d good energy. \n\nPresented by **Emerald Sky and Papa’s Herb**\, this 
 experience is your invitation to slow down\, light up\, and turn elevated 
 moments into art—Mercy style.\n\n**Date & Time**\n\n**Date:** Sunday\, A
 pril 12\, 2026\n\n**Time:** 12:00 pm - 4:00 pm\n\n**What’s Included**\n\
 nAll painting supplies\n\nChill\, guided creative session — zero pressur
 e\, all fun and you get to take home your masterpiece\n\nAn atmosphere buz
 zing with smooth evening beats\n\nA cannabis-friendly lounge to spark your
  creativity\n\n**Ticket Tiers**\n\n**General Admission - $35:** Paint Supp
 lies Only\n\n**VIP Tier 1 - $50:** Includes a 🌱$25 Goodie Bag \n\n**VI
 P Tier 2 - $75:** Includes a 🌱$50 Goodie Bag \n\n21+ Only | DCC # C12-
 0000420-LIC
LOCATION:The Lounge at Mercy
URL:https://www.themercylounge.com
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
