UID:260216KT_sz7cKgEKBUsIEheraNQ
DESCRIPTION:Going head-to-head with an old enemy-and renowned assassin. Re
 gister here: Join us in conversation with acclaimed author Brad Taylor on 
 his latest work\, Shadow Strike\, book 20 of the bestselling Pike Logan se
 ries. A rogue Iranian group orchestrates a plot to strike back at enemies\
 , beginning with the assassination of the Israeli prime minister. Pike Log
 an is tasked with hunting down the Ghost\, leading the Taskforce to Argent
 ina in a race against time. About the Author: Brad Taylor is the author of
  the New York Times bestselling Pike Logan series. He served for more than
  twenty years in the U.S. Army\, including eight years in 1st Special Forc
 es Operational Detachment-Delta\, commonly known as Delta Force. He retire
 d as a Special Forces lieutenant colonel and now lives in Charleston\, Sou
 th Carolina.
