SUMMARY:FREE Advance Directive Health Care Planning Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260416T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260416T160000
UID:2602259B5cSJRxnUys_T7_ArwgcQ
DESCRIPTION:An advance directive is an important document for all adults a
 ge 18 and older. It helps you share your healthcare wishes and name someon
 e you trust to make medical decisions for you if you’re ever unable to s
 peak for yourself.\n\nAt these workshops\, we will explain what an advance
  directive is and provide you with help to complete the form.\n\nFree Nota
 ry Public services will be available to get your advance directive documen
 t notarized at no cost to you. Please bring a valid photo ID (driver’s l
 icense or passport) if you plan to have your document notarized.\n\nSpanis
 h interpreters will be available at both workshops.\n\nJoin us on either A
 pril 16 or April 28 and give your loved ones the peace of mind that comes 
 from knowing your healthcare wishes in advance.\n\nEvent provided by the P
 rovidence Sonoma County Inpatient Palliative Care Team.
LOCATION:Providence Santa Rosa Memorial Hospital 
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/free-advance-directive-
 health-care-planning-workshop/18185933/2026-04-16T12
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
