 che knitting? In this workshop\, you’ll learn the fundamentals of this b
 eautifully textured technique while starting a cozy two-color cowl. Brioch
 e creates a lofty\, reversible fabric that looks complex but becomes rhyth
 mic once you understand the structure.\n\n**In this workshop you’ll:**\n
 \n• Learn the basics of brioche knitting\n\n• Practice brioche knit (B
 RK) and brioche purl (BRP)\n\n• Work two-color brioche in the round\n\n
