DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T220000
UID:2603318EEAwGakIEOdgA4Q076Y3w
DESCRIPTION:**The Roaring 420’s: Great Gatsby Party**\n\nStep into a wor
 ld of decadence\, indulgence\, and elevated highs at Mercy’s Roaring 420
 ’s Gatsby Costume Party—a fully immersive 1920s-inspired cannabis expe
 rience inside The Lounge.\n\nOn **Saturday\, April 18th from 6PM – 10PM*
 *\, we’re transforming the space into a lavish Gatsby-era affair where l
 uxury meets smoke-filled sophistication. Velvet nights\, golden details\, 
 and jazz-era energy set the tone—brought to life by a live performance f
 rom **Fog City Swing**\, delivering a one-of-a-kind soundtrack of classic 
 swing\, modern hits\, and big band flair. Their signature “smallest big 
 band” sound creates an electric\, dance-worthy atmosphere you won’t fi
 nd anywhere else.\n\nYour ticket includes a **full dinner experience\, a 
 curated goodie bag\, and your own assigned seat**—so you can settle in a
 nd enjoy the night in style.\n\nThis isn’t just a party—it’s an expe
 rience.\n\nSip on **herbal cannabis-infused cocktails**\, explore **inte
 ractive brand stations**\, and indulge in **guided tasting options** desi
 gned to elevate your palate. Watch the craft come alive at our **live joi
 nt rolling area**\, try your luck with **casino-style games**\, and disco
 ver curated moments of entertainment throughout the night.\n\nAnd of cours
 e—**dress to impress.**\n\nWe’re hosting a **Gatsby Costume Contest**
 \, so come in your finest flapper dresses\, sharpest suits\, and boldest 1
 920s looks for a chance to stand out and take the spotlight for the night.
 \n\nThis is a **fully immersive themed experience**\, and guests are high
 ly encouraged to participate in the dress code to bring the night to life.
 \n\n**Date & Time**\n\n**Date:** Saturday\, April 18\, 2026\n\n**Time:** 6
 :00 - 10:00 PM\n\n**Ticket Tiers**\n\n🎷 **$100 Reserved Inside Seating 
 Ticket.** Perfect for guests who want premium comfort and a front-row seat
  to the night’s festivities. Enjoy the full Gatsby treatment with **rese
 rved indoor seating** in the heart of the action. Ticket includes: gourmet
  dinner\, exclusive goodie bag & access to the immersive Roaring 420’s e
 xperience\n\n🌿 **$75 Open Outside Seating Ticket.** Ideal for a more re
 laxed\, social vibe under the night sky. Soak in the atmosphere with **ope
 n outdoor seating** while still enjoying all the indulgences of the evenin
 g. Ticket includes: gourmet dinner\, exclusive goodie bag & access to the 
 immersive Roaring 420’s experience\n\n21+ Only | DCC # C12-0000420-LIC
LOCATION:The Lounge at Mercy
URL:https://www.themercylounge.com
