DESCRIPTION:The Laugh Cellar presents: Headliner Nancy Norton \n\nHistori
 c Wine Tool Museum at Buena Vista Winery \n\nColorado-based headliner Nan
 cy Norton can boast winning Best of the Fest alongside Jay Leno at the Bur
 bank Comedy Festival. She is the champion of the 40th Annual Seattle Inter
 national Comedy Competition and made history as the first woman to win the
  Boston Comedy Festival. High-energy and fast-paced\, this award-winning c
 omedian connects effortlessly with audiences of all ages. Nancy has an unc
 anny ability to read the room\, weaving spontaneous moments into a uniquel
 y interactive performance. Some even call it a healing experience.\n\nComp
 limentary parking on-site\n\nIndoor event\, theater style seating \n\nDo
 ors 6:00pm  / Showtime 7:00pm\n\nAVAILABLE FOR PURCHASE: \n\nA delicious
  selection of wine and sparkling wine by the bottle and glass\n\nOakville 
 Cheese & Charcuterie trays\n\nPlease no outside alcohol\n\nNo pets\, servi
 ce dogs ok - please provide valid license\n\nShow is open to an audience 2
 1+
LOCATION:Buena Vista Historical Winery
URL:https://www.crushersofcomedy.com/april182026-780104.html
