BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Healthy Kids Day at the Marin Y
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T160000
UID:260312iiV-0bm5xUq2Pisss9iUfg
DESCRIPTION:The Marin Y Invites Families to Kick Off a Healthy\, Active Su
 mmer at 2026 Healthy Kids Day \n\nFree and open to the public\, this annu
 al event features a day of fun-filled activities to celebrate kids being k
 ids \n\nThe Marin Y\, part of the YMCA of Greater San Francisco charitabl
 e organization\, will be hosting the Y’s annual Healthy Kids Day on Sat
 urday April 18th from 11am-4pm\, located at your local Marin Y facility
 \, 1500 Los Gamos Drive in San Rafael. This free\, annual event feature
 s a variety of family-friendly activities to encourage healthy kids\, hea
 lthy families and a healthy start to the summer season. \n\nHealthy K
 ids Day’s mission is to prepare Marin families for a safe\, healthy 
 and fun summer. Some featured activities include: \n\nFree recreational 
 swim for kids starting at 12:30pm \n\nFree swim assessments for kids star
 ting at 1pm \n\nAn Open House of the full Marin Y facility & offerings \
 n\nA full schedule of free class demonstrations  \n\nA bounce house \n\
 nFree smoothies made by you via bike pedal power \n\nA host of local comm
 unity resources that support healthy living for families \n\nCrafts\, fac
 epainting\, and STEM project-making \n\nGames\, obstacle courses\, hoop c
 ontests\, and more \n\nThe first hundred families that come will receive 
 a free swag bag. Families who fill out their Healthy Kids Day “passpo
 rt” at the event will be entered into a raffle to win a free three-mo
 nth household membership to the Marin Y\, including access to the pool and
  classes and wellness offerings.
LOCATION:Marin YMCA
URL:https://marinymca.wixsite.com/healthy-kids-day
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Butter and Egg Days Parade 2026
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260418T170000
UID:260311_o0rOTKZYkOoHuWOrZ501w
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to be transported to a world of wonder at the 43rd A
 nnual Butter & Egg Days Parade in Petaluma! Americas' Birthday - Petaluma 
 Style" celebrates the nation's 250th Birthday by honoring Petaluma's deep 
 agricultural roots and hometown spirit. This year's Butter & Egg Days Para
 de recognizes the farmers\, families\, imigrants\, makers\, entrepreneurs\
 , and creatives whose hard work\, imagination\, and ingenuity reflect the 
 enduring American Dream. This celebration also pays respect to the Indigen
 ous peoples who first stewarded this land\, the courage of our founders\, 
 and the dedication of the dairy and egg farming community that shaped our 
 town. Rooted in community\, innovation\, and independence\, the parade cel
 ebrates the small-town spirit that continues to make Petaluma a vibrant pl
 ace to call home. Head to Downtown Petaluma and celebrate with our communi
 ty on this day of fun\, history\, and local pride! Parade starts at noon. 
 The parade is surrounded by aFestivalthat spreads over four city blocks fr
 om 10am-5pm offering a wide variety of food\, crafts\, beverage gardens\, 
 two large kid areas\, live music\, and more! This annual event aims to bri
 ng together the community for a day of fun and entertainment.
LOCATION:Downtown Petaluma Historic Petaluma Petaluma
URL:https://www.marinmommies.com/calendar/butter-and-egg-days-parade-2026
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
