DESCRIPTION:**The Annadel Half Marathon is a non-profit fundraising event.
  Over the past 16 years\, we have raised funds to make the park a more bea
 utiful place for all to enjoy!   The Half Marathon course is a hilly\, a
 nd technical course designed for the experienced trail runner looking for 
 a challenge. Enjoy gorgeous scenery with green meadows\, wild flowers\, an
 d variety of beautiful trees. The race starts at the Spring Lake Oak Knoll
 s picnic area and winds through Spring Lake Park before climbing into Anna
 del State Park. The Annadel Half Marathon is a tough course with over 1\,5
 00 feet of elevation gain over rocky and rooted terrain. The 5k course is 
 an out and back route heading up a gravel fire road slightly into Annadel 
 State park.**
