DESCRIPTION:Directions:\n\nMeet at the gate on San Carlos Way in Novato. F
 rom Hwy 101 in Novato\, take the exit for San Marin Dr west 2.1 miles. Tur
 n right onto San Carlos Way and follow to end \\(dead end\\).\n\nSponsor: 
 Parks\n\nAccommodation Information: If you are a person with a disability 
