 nd look at some core native plants that are easy to care for and make grea
 t additions to any existing garden. Registration Encouraged: Go to sonomam
 g.ucanr.edu Upcoming Events to complete your registration. After registeri
 ng\, you will receive a confirmation email containing information about at
