DESCRIPTION:Restorative Yamuna Body Rolling\n\nOn the Mat in the EESystem
 ™ with Jacque Benton\n\nSunday\, March 22 11:00 AM- 1:00 PM • $45\n\nO
 NLY 16 SPOTS AVAILABLE If you do not already have an account with Energy W
 ave Center\, you will be prompted to join free to purchase.\n\nYamuna Body
  Rolling \\(YBR\\) releases tension in the body while creating strength an
 d flexibility. Using a Yamuna ball\, we will anatomically roll through tig
 ht and misaligned muscles. This creates Body Sustainability by working out
  stiffness and improves range of motion by creating space in the body. YBR
  can help prevent injuries and heal breakdowns.\n\nCombining the EESystem
 ™ and YamunaBody Rolling helps the body release on a deeper level.\n\n 
 During this class you will learn how to utilize your Yamuna Body Rolling s
 kills in bed.\n\nLearn to align and release tension from your body in the 
 comfort of your own bed. \n\n- Do it early in the morning to start your 
 day fresh and flexible\n\n- Do it at night to release tension and stress 
 from the day\n\n- Do it in the middle of the night to help get back to sl
 eep\n\n- Do it anytime to relax and unwind \n\nDETAILS:\n\n- Yamuna ball
 s will be provided or bring your own\n\n- Please bring a yoga mat\n\n- Wea
 r comfortable close fitting yoga type clothing\n\n- To participate\, you m
 ust be able to get down on the floor and back up from it\n\nExperience the
  Energy Enhancement System™ \\(EESystem\\) as you rest in this supportiv
 e scalar field. Many experience profound relaxation\, cellular rejuvenatio
 n amplifying the effects of Yamuna Body Rolling.\n\nABOUT YOUR INSTRUCTOR 
 Jacque Benton has been teaching weekly Yamuna Body Rolling classes since 
 2004. Practicing Massage therapy for over 20 years & teaching Yoga\, combi
 ned with a fascination with anatomy\, fuels Jacque’s passion for teachin
 g Yamuna. Jacque is a certified Yamuna Teacher Trainer and holds annual tr
 ainings in the area.
