DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260419T150000
UID:260326QPC3CHN6jUyNFTkc_m7VDg
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever wondered what it is like to be a winemaker? This
  is your invitation to step into the cellar with Lynmar Estate Winemaker P
 ete Soergel for an immersive journey into the art and science of crafting 
 exceptional wine. \n\nYour experience begins with an exclusive tour of ou
 r production facilities\, followed by a hands-on blending seminar. Taste a
 nd blend four distinct barrel samples to create your own unique cuvée alo
 ngside fellow members. Pete will evaluate the blends and select one as a p
 otential candidate for the 2025 vintage.\n\nAfter your time in the cellar\
 , gather for a thoughtfully prepared lunch paired with finished wines\, co
 ntinuing the conversation about the magical transformation from grape to g
 lass. As always\, the afternoon concludes in true Lynmar fashion with beau
 tiful food\, extraordinary wine\, wonderful company\, and memories in the 
 making. \n\nFor added ease and enjoyment\, round-trip transportation from
  San Francisco is available for guests who prefer not to drive.\n\nPrice i
 ncludes guided tour\, wine\, food\, and community. Space is limited\, so r
 eserve your spot today!
LOCATION:Lynmar Estate
URL:https://lynmarestate.com/reservation/type/winemaker-luncheon/?reservat
 ionDate=2026-04-19&guestCount=2&reservationTime=11%3A00%3A00  
