DESCRIPTION:Guided by our Estate Garden Host\, guests will embark on a sen
 sory journey through Raymond Vineyards’ gardens and vineyards\, discover
 ing the rhythms of the land\, sustainable practices\, and the living ecosy
 stem that shapes every bottle we produce.\n\nAlong the way\, sip wines cra
 fted from the very vineyards beneath your feet\, allowing each pour to ref
 lect its place\, season\, and soil. The journey concludes with a thoughtfu
 lly curated cheese and charcuterie experience\, designed to complement the
  wines and invite guests to linger\, connect\, and celebrate the beauty of
  the natural world.\n\nThis Earth Day\, slow down\, engage your senses\, a
 nd honor the land that gives us so much.
LOCATION:Raymond Vineyards
