BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Spirit Sisters
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260419T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260419T150000
UID:250710jX9xT03MiUSh4iernF-Grg
DESCRIPTION:SPIRIT SISTERS REIKI SHARE10AM - 12PM\n\nJoin us for a Reiki s
 hare to embrace\n\nEmbrace and share the power of energy healing\, conveni
 ently timed right before our monthly sister circle!\n\nJoin us as we excha
 nge Reiki Energy Healing with one another\, to support\, heal and empower 
 each other! This is a great opportunity to practice your Reiki or energy h
 ealing gifts in a safe communal space.\n\nRelease stress\, restore balance
  and recharge your body\, mind and spirit with our magical Reiki Circle. I
 t consists of many healing hands on one person at a time.\n\nEach share wi
 ll start with a general introduction\, then the circle will be grounded by
  one of our masters with a guided meditation\, followed by treatments unti
 l each person has had a chance to receive healing.\n\nThis is a time and s
 pace for teachers\, practitioners\, those who are interested in sharing in
  connection and healing\, as well as anyone who would like to learn more a
 bout Reiki.\n\nBring:\n\n- A water bottle for yourself to replenish and hy
 drate\n\n- Any healing tools such as tuning forks\, crystals\, etc. that y
 ou may want to use\n\n- A $1 minimum cash\, Venmo or PayPal donation\n\nJo
 in us afterwards for our monthly sister circle!\n\nSpirit Sisters of Sonom
 a County is a spiritually based women's group for aligned women to be thei
 r true\, authentic selves. Our events are to empower and connect with like
 -minded women in a safe and sacred space. Learn more about Spirit Sisters 
 of Sonoma County at\n\nspiritsistersinc.org .\n\n\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\
 \_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\n\n\\_\\
 _\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\
 \_\\_\n\nSPIRIT SISTERS CIRCLE - 12:15PM - 3PM\n\nFor our March Sister Cir
 cle\, we are honored to have community member Tara leading an Intuitive Ar
 t workshop!\n\nIn this workshop\, you will learn how to use your intuition
  and expression in an artistic way. Through art\, you'll learn how you can
  heal\, play\, transform and find answers within yourself!\n\nNo art exper
 ience necessary!\n\nBring:\n\n- A Vegan Potluck Item\n\n- A $1 minimum don
 ation\n\nPlease:\n\n• We want anyone who is called to join us\, and we'd
  rather you come late than not at all! We request that if you are running 
 late\, please enter through the front door of the building and enter the s
 choolhouse room quietly to prevent significant disruption to the group.\n\
 n• Due to our circles being a safe space for women to get vulnerable\, t
 his is an adult woman only event.\n\nAbout the Sponsored Circle Host: Tara
  Dickinson\n\nTara grew up in an ashram \\(intentional community\\) with a
  spiritual teacher whose main message was kindness\, feed everyone \\(body
 \, mind & soul\\)\, and serve. Through these decades of inner work\, silen
 t meditation\, and awareness\, she can hold a space of stillness & underst
 anding for others while we dive into what wants to be expressed.\n\nWith a
  background in fine arts and years of teaching a variety of art labs to ki
 ds & grownups\, Tara enjoys sharing tools to help everyone feel comfortabl
 e in the creative process while learning new techniques.\n\nTara holds a B
 achelor's in Fine Arts and works to combine her education and life experie
 nces to create programs that encourage people to live their best lives by 
 minimizing stress\, opening to awareness\, and making choices that are tai
 lored to their needs and lifestyle.\n\nMore info can be learned at\n\nSpir
 it Sisters of Sonoma County is a spiritually based women's group for align
 ed women to be their true\, authentic selves. Our events are to empower an
 d connect with like-minded women in a safe and sacred space. Learn more ab
 out Spirit Sisters of Sonoma County at\n\nspiritsistersinc.org .
LOCATION:Arlene Francis Center for Spirit\, Art\, and Politics
URL:http://spiritsistersinc.org/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
