DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260420T200000
UID:260405vSGL8STjwk6YxG6ubrhwdg
DESCRIPTION:420 REGGAE PARTY at The Lounge at Mercy\n\nMonday\, April 20th
  | 1:00PM – 8:00PM\n\nDAY 4 of 420 = FREE ENTRY • ALL DAY VIBES\n\nGet
  ready to celebrate 420 in true island style at The Lounge at Mercy! We’
 re bringing you a full day of reggae rhythms\, good energy\, and elevated 
 vibes from start to finish.\n\nStep into a laid-back atmosphere filled wit
 h music\, community\, and positive vibrations as we turn up the groove all
  day long.\n\nLIVE MUSIC ALL DAY\n\nWe’re stacking the stage with an inc
 redible lineup of reggae talent:\n\nHeadliner: Garden Grove – Sublime Tr
 ibute Band\n\nExperience the ultimate tribute to Sublime with Garden Grove
 \, delivering all the iconic hits and feel-good SoCal reggae vibes you kno
 w and love. Expect a nostalgic\, high-energy set that’ll have everyone s
 inging along.\n\nFeaturing:\n\nBobby Tenna – Smooth vocals and soulful r
 eggae sounds\n\nKool Vibes Band – Our house Reggae band bringing infecti
 ous rhythms and feel-good energy\n\nJah Yzer – Roots-driven reggae with 
 powerful presence\n\nFrom chill grooves to dance-worthy beats\, the music 
 keeps flowing all day.\n\nEVENT HIGHLIGHTS\n\n🎶 Live reggae performance
 s from 1PM–8PM\n\n🌿 30+ Brands\, Food & Craft Vendors in a 420-friend
