BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:We The Sculptors…International Sculpture Days
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T160000
UID:260331PAAU6ISEGEeA73sLMM9FZg
DESCRIPTION:From ancient monuments carved in stone to bold contemporary ab
 straction\, sculpture has always been a defiant presence in the world. It 
 occupies space and refuses to be ignored.\n\nThis year’s International S
 culpture Days event embraces the belief that sculpture can inspire\, provo
 ke\, and challenge the world around us. Ten Artists will present their wor
 k \, and visitors can engage in acts of “defiant dissidence\,” explori
 ng how art can serve as both personal reflection and public voice.\n\nThe 
 event draws on a long tradition of artists and citizens using visual langu
 age to express dissent\, question norms\, and imagine new possibilities. A
 t its core\, We The Sculptors affirms the enduring role of artists to chal
 lenge\, to question\, and to stand visibly in the public square.
LOCATION:T Barny Gallery & Sculpture Garden
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/we-the-sculptors-intern
 ational-sculpture-days/18433856/2026-04-25T11
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
