BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:10\,000 Degrees Annual Gala: One Amazing Community
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T210000
UID:260224OR7qVI2ws0afdY-Gsj2_1Q
DESCRIPTION:10\,000 Degrees hosts its annual fundraising gala ‘ONE Amazi
 ng Community’ on Saturday\, April 25\, 2026\, at the Marin Civic Center 
 Exhibit Hall in San Rafael.\n\nThe ‘ONE Amazing Community’ gala will c
 elebrate and recognize the contributions of many in the community who have
  played a role in helping achieve educational equity and in supporting stu
 dents from low-income backgrounds to fulfill their dreams of becoming coll
 ege graduates. Proceeds from the gala will benefit students and programs a
 cross the eight Bay Area counties that 10\,000 Degrees serves.\n\nGuests a
 ttending the 10\,000 Degrees ‘ONE Amazing Community’ gala will enjoy a
  cocktail reception\, a seated dinner\, and an inspirational program featu
 ring special guests\, followed by a festive after-party.\n\n*About 10\,000
  Degrees*\n\n*Bay Area nonprofit 10\,000 Degrees is unlocking student succ
 ess by giving more students equitable opportunities for a quality college 
 education and career success. The organization brings a proven model\, dat
 a-driven outcomes\, and a seasoned leadership team to create educational o
 pportunities for students from low-income backgrounds. 10\,000 Degrees rea
 ches over 16\,000 students and families annually\, including 4\,200 colleg
 e students attending universities and institutions across the nation.*
LOCATION:Marin Civic Center Exhibit Hall 
URL:https://10000degrees.org/event-landing-page-template/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
