DESCRIPTION:*Where unforgettable wines\, live music\, and good vibes come 
 together.*\n\nJoin us every Saturday from 3–6 PM at Spicy Vines for a ta
 sting room experience like no other — where top local musicians from acr
 oss the Bay Area meet our award-winning small-lot wines. From Rock & Roll 
 and Blues to Jazz\, Bluegrass\, and Americana\, each weekend brings new so
 unds and new reasons to raise a glass. \n\n**The Beguilers** The Beguiler
 s are a swing jazz quintet with a French flair\, blending romantic\, fun\
 , and timeless tunes from the 1930s–1960s with a playful gypsy jazz styl
 e. \n\n**Details**\n\nNo cover. Walk-ins are welcome\, but this event ten
 ds to fill up quickly\, so we recommend making a reservation. We are dog a
 nd family friendly!
LOCATION:Spicy Vines Winery
URL:https://spicyvines.com/event/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Opera Film:  TURANDOT from Bregenz Festival
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T133000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T154500
UID:2601133PMyvQiOXkyXdc9WkiS0AQ
DESCRIPTION:One of the world’s most famous arias comes from the
  composer’s final opera\, Turandot: “Nessun dorma” – none
  shall sleep because by morning the Chinese princess is determin
 ed to have discovered the name of the unknown  prince. The work
  is remarkable for its Chinese local color\, its opulent crowd 
 scenes\, its powerful choruses and its characters overwhelmed by 
 their emotions. Giacomo Puccini's masterpiece is 100 years old on
  04/25/26.  Celebrate with The Jarvis Conservatory by watching one of
  their favorite previous productions: Bregenz Festival - Seebühne
 . Projected with the latest in digital cinema technology.
LOCATION:Jarvis Conservatory
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/opera-film-turandot-fro
 m-bregenz-festival/17865939/2026-04-25T13
