SUMMARY:Classic Chrome | Unwind Weekend Event
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T160000
UID:260329HhnLqWz7zUWVakGOUR-UKQ
DESCRIPTION:The Classic Car Show of Calistoga is a beloved community tradi
 tion and a highlight of Unwind Weekend. Set in the heart of downtown Calis
 toga\, the show celebrates the timeless beauty and craftsmanship of classi
 c automobiles manufactured prior to 1980. Stroll among rows of meticulousl
 y maintained vintage vehicles\, meet the proud owners\, and soak in the re
 laxed Napa Valley atmosphere. Local food and beverage options will be avai
 lable nearby\, or bring a picnic\, settle in\, and enjoy an afternoon surr
 ounded by chrome\, curves\, and nostalgia. Cars are not formally judged\, 
 though informal People’s Choice recognition may add to the fun. If you a
 re the proud owner of a classic car\, we invite you to submit your applica
 tion and be part of this special weekend. The show is open to the public\,
  and admission is free.
LOCATION:Downtown Calistoga
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/4147681032151891/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Calistoga Unwind Weekend
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T200000
UID:26032953-iIP53ZEKUDvlL-mQghA
DESCRIPTION:Classic Chrome | Bathrobe Chic Join us for Unwind Weekend!  Fo
 r more than 150 years\, Calistoga has been a place where people come to sl
 ow down\, soak\, sip\, and truly unwind. From natural hot springs and mud 
 baths to long afternoons in tasting rooms and strolls through our historic
  downtown\, relaxation isn’t a trend here\; it’s our heritage. Unwind 
 Weekend celebrates that spirit in the most Calistoga way possible: playful
 \, elevated\, and effortlessly charming. Saturday kicks off with a Classic
  Car Show on Cedar Street — vintage style\, community energy\, and a nod
  to timeless California cool. And as evening settles in\, the Bathrobe Bar
  Crawl invites guests to do what Calistoga has always done best: slip into
  something comfortable and enjoy great food\, great drinks\, and great com
 pany. This isn’t just a series of events. It’s a weekend designed arou
 nd staying\, playing\, and unwinding in Napa Valley’s original wellness 
 destination.
LOCATION:Downtown Calistoga
URL:https://www.facebook.com/events/1605099354029871/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
