DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260426T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260426T150000
UID:260324_X3om4NRfEyF0w3GuuV08Q
DESCRIPTION:We invite you to spend a day on the land\, resting in the Budd
 ha’s teachings on wisdom and kindness. Together\, we will practice culti
 vating kind awareness that supports us in growing our capacity to meet the
  joys and challenges of being human. As we learn to steadily meet things a
 s they are\, the wisdom of the Dhamma unfolds\, and through this cultivati
 on we touch into the possibility of freedom.\n\nThe day will include guide
 d sitting and Dhamma reflections and opportunity for walking meditations. 
 The day will be held mostly in silence\, with a few intentional moments fo
 r community connection and shared reflection.
LOCATION:Spirit Rock Meditation Center
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/cultivating-a-wise-and-
 kind-heart/18363189/2026-04-26T10
