DESCRIPTION:Our Community\, Our Family\n\nCelebrating Together\n\nAs a fam
 ily and a wider community\, we share our strongest bonds when we break bre
 ad together. That is made all the sweeter when we can also contribute to t
 he greater good in the world through this simple act. Come eat\, celebrate
  and listen to the best musical artists in our region\, and perhaps\, the 
 world\, with all your generous neighbors as we make good for others who ne
 ed our help. Contribute to our cause because SONOMA CARES! Visit our websi
 te for more information and a link to our tickets. Get yours soon before t
 hey are gone!
LOCATION:Freidman Event Center
