BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Symphony Pops: Symphonic Genesis–Tribute to Phil Collins
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260426T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260426T150000
UID:2507228IMQoJev_k28uq5Sy6OKBw
DESCRIPTION:Back to All Shows\n\nSymphony Pops\n\nSymphonic Genesis–Trib
 ute to Phil Collins\n\nStuart Chafetz\, Guest Conductor\n\nAaron Finley an
 d Brook Wood\, Vocalists\n\nBrian Kushmaul\, Drummer\n\nSunday\, April 26\
 , 2026\n\n3:00 pm\n\n2:00 pm Pre-Show Discussion\n\nBUY TICKETS  \n\n \n\n
 Phil Collins’ one-of-a-kind drum work and songwriting have left an endur
 ing mark on music. Collins and his Genesis bandmates\, Tony Banks and Mike
  Rutherford\, penned unforgettable hits featured in this symphonic tribute
 . Accompanied by vocalists Aaron Finley and Brook Wood\, along with drumme
 r Brian Kushmaul\, Guest Conductor Stuart Chafetz will lead some of the be
 st of the best\, including “Follow You Follow Me\,” “Abacab\,” “
 I Missed Again\,” “Turn It On Again\,” “Sussudio\,” “One More 
 Night\,” “Take Me Home\,” “Two Hearts\,” and the iconic “In th
 e Air Tonight.” \n\nGenerous support provided by Nancy & Michael Hall\, 
 Betty & George Ferris \n\nSymphony Pops Series\n\nSee the full series here
 : Symphony Pops Series \n\nSeason ticket packages are available ONLINE now
 \, or by downloading the form and sending the completed form to us by mail
  or email. See details on the form. If you have any questions\, call the P
 atron & Member Services Office at 707.546.3600. Order today to get the bes
 t seats! \n\nRenew online\n\nDownload New Subscription Form\n\n \n\nTHIRD 
 PARTY RESELLERS\n\nDon’t get taken by deceptive online resellers who use
  bots to buy tickets and then mark up their prices. The only safe way to p
 rotect your purchase and guarantee the best seats at the lowest cost is to
  work directly with us: through our website\, by phone\, or at our box off
 ice in Santa Rosa. Plus\, we’re not bots. Our friendly team members are 
 easily accessible by phone or at the box office to provide customer suppor
 t.
LOCATION:Luther Burbank Center for the Arts
URL:https://lutherburbankcenter.org/event/symphonic-genesis-and-phil-colli
 ns/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
