 00 PM\n\nLocation\n\nRoom 208\n\nExperience Level\n\nBeginning and Interme
 diate\n\nDrawing & Painting\, Extended Classes\n\nAge\\(s\\)\n\n18 and old
 er\n\nRegistration Cost:\n\n$290\n\nMaterials Fee:\n\nIncluded\n\nTotal Re
 gistration Cost:\n\n$290Explore soft pastel techniques while creating land
 scapes\, still lifes & more. Guided lessons for all skill levels\; no expe
 rience needed.\n\nAbout the Class\n\nThis class will introduce students to
  basic techniques of using soft pastels as they work alongside the instruc
 tor to create landscapes\, still lifes\, animals and flowers. Learn to lay
 er colors to create luminous\, painterly effects. Beginners are guided as 
