DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260427T000000
UID:2602243qp96CNgh0-UQb9Ny-8WSg
DESCRIPTION:Step into a palace in time with other Jewish communal professi
 onals from your region. Enjoy 3 days of rest\, movement\, and Jewish artis
 tic and creative practices in an idyllic setting.\n\nForge meaningful rela
 tionships with colleagues in your region while engaging with powerful reli
 gious and spiritual practice and Jewish learning.\n\nParticipants will eme
 rge with a broader network of friends and allies in the field\, new Jewish
  wisdom sources for inspiration\, and renewed motivation\, passion\, and c
 ommitment to their work. We will talk\, sing\, pray\, move our bodies indo
 ors and outside\, eat delicious food\, rest\, laugh\, and reflect.  With g
 uest educators Rabbi Deborah Sacks Mintz\, Wendy Verba\, and Shimon Darwic
 k Brinbaum.
LOCATION:URJ Camp Newman
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/107727410?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
