 y’s years of expertise in the field and enjoy creating handbuilt\, throw
 n\, and altered forms. Amy caters each syllabus closely to her group of st
 udents\, ensuring that every project fits the desires of participants. Thi
 s course encourages folks to work on independent projects in the class\, r
 eceiving one on one support from Amy throughout the time. This course will
