UID:251209hSN6EatSlUaNiGPGwzYo-Q
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special evening with THE WEDDING PRESENT with su
 pport by MARK ROBINSON SINGS UNREST\n\npresented by \\(\\(\\(folkYeah!\\)\
 \)\\) and Gundlach Bundschu Winery \n\nWHEN: Wednesday\, April 29th 2026 \
 n\nWHERE: GB Redwood Barn \n\nTIME: Doors 7pm | Show 8pm \n\nPRICE: $79 \n
 \nBUY TICKETS\n\nFood available for purchase \\(vendors will be announced 
 prior to the show\\) \n\n  \n\nTICKETING:\n\nHave your ticket ready when 
 you arrive! If you opted for mobile delivery\, please make sure it’s rea
 dy to go on your phone. Printed tickets? Have them out and ready to be sca
 nned. Bacchus Club members\, enjoy express entry with your special line. \
 n\nPARKING:\n\nParking is complimentary for Bacchus Wine Club members. To 
 encourage carpooling\, we offer free parking to vehicles with 3\\+ passeng
 ers\, full 2-seaters\, motorcycles\, and electric vehicles. Otherwise\, pa
 rking will be $16.50 pre-paid in advance or $20 \\(cash only\\) at entry. 
 For ADA accommodations please let the parking attendant know. \n\nPLEASE N
 O:\n\nCoolers\n\nWater \\(bring an empty bottle as we have filtered re-fil
 l stations\\)\n\nPets\n\nChairs with legs of any length \\(stadium seats t
 hat sit flat on the ground are permitted\\)\n\nOutside food or drink\n\nBa
 d Attitudes… this is Rhinefarm after all\n\nACCESSIBILITY:\n\nFor any q
 uestions regarding ADA accommodations related to parking\, seating\, restr
 ooms\, etc. please contact us at info@gunbun.com or 707.938.5277. \n\nYOUR
  EXPERIENCE\, YOUR ADVENTURE:\n\nAt Gundlach Bundschu Winery\, we invite y
 ou to immerse yourself in the magic of our historic Redwood Barn\, where t
 he beauty of nature blends with unforgettable performances. As with all gr
 eat adventures\, attending an outdoor event carries a touch of unpredictab
 ility. \n\nWhether it’s the rustle of the vines in the breeze\, the gent
 le slope of the hillside\, or the surprises nature has in store\, we encou
 rage you to embrace the moment. While we strive to create a safe and enjoy
 able environment\, the great outdoors brings its own set of risks. By join
 ing us\, you understand and accept the inherent possibilities\, but not li
 mited to\, uneven ground\, changing weather\, and the occasional visit fro
 m our local wildlife. We ask that you tread carefully\, come prepared for 
 all conditions\, and remember to look after yourself and your belongings. 
 \n\nBy attending our events\, you acknowledge that your participation is v
 oluntary\, and you assume all responsibility for any personal injuries\, a
 ccidents\, or loss of property that may occur during your time with us. Gu
 ndlach Bundschu Winery and its team are dedicated to your safety\, but can
 not be held liable for incidents that may arise from the natural elements 
 of this experience. \n\nIn purchasing a ticket and joining us under the op
 en sky\, you agree to these terms and release Gundlach Bundschu Winery fro
 m any claims or liabilities associated with the inherent risks of an outdo
 or gathering. We look forward to sharing this special place with you\, whe
 re every moment is part of the journey. \n\nMAKE SURE TO VISIT OUR VENUE I
 NFORMATION PAGE – HERE\n\nVENUE MAP
LOCATION:Gundlach Bundschu Winery
URL:https://www.gunbun.com/event/wedding-present/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
