DESCRIPTION:Pawsport Napa Valley 2026\n\nPURCHASE YOUR PAWSPORT HERE: http
 s://napahumane.org/events/pawsport/\n\nWhat Your Pawsport Unlocks: • One
  complimentary wine tasting per Pawsport holder at each participating wine
 ry • Access to a curated lineup of dog-friendly Napa Valley wineries\n\n
 How to Use Your Pawsport: • Your Pawsport is valid March 1–April 30\, 
 2026 with one tasting per person\, per winery • Be sure to check each wi
 nery’s hours and reservation requirements before visiting\, as many loca
 tions do require reservations\n\nYour Impact: Every Pawsport supports Napa
  Humane’s Power of Prevention—helping fund lifesaving spay and neuter 
 surgeries and preventive care that reduce overpopulation and prevent suffe
 ring. Together\, Pawsport supporters help make it possible to fund up to 2
 46 days of lifesaving surgery each year\, creating a lasting impact for an
 imal welfare in Napa County.\n\nReady to Sip for a Cause? Grab your Pawspo
 rt\, explore Napa Valley wineries\, and enjoy complimentary tastings all w
 hile helping protect pets through prevention-focused care. Don’t forget 
 to share your adventures using \\#PawsportNapaValley and by tagging @napah
 umane.\n\nThank you for helping make Napa Valley a more compassionate plac
 e for pets and the people who love them—we can’t wait to raise a glass
  with you this spring! 🐾🍷\n\nHave a question? Contact Gillian Ferro 
 at gferro@napahumane.org or by phone at \\(707\\) 255-8118 x205.
LOCATION:Napa Valley
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/pawsport-napa-valley-20
 26/18117345/2026-04-30T00
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
