 hearsals are every Thursday through June 8th. Have questions or want perfo
 rmance dates? Just send us an email! info@singnapavalley.org RSVP your int
 erest using this link and we’ll get back to you with all the details. ht
 tps://www.zeffy.com/en-US/newsletter-form/rsvp-to-singing-in-the-2026-spri
 ngsummer-session-with-sing-napa-valley\n\n**Let’s make beautiful music t
